http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/DISC/Translation+of+content

{panel:title=Atlassian Status as of 18 October 2013|borderStyle=solid|borderColor=#3C78B5|titleBGColor=#3C78B5|bgColor=#E7F4FA}
Hi Everyone,

Thanks for your continued feedback on this issue. In the interest of transparency, we are closing this issue as it's not on the near term roadmap to implement. While there are many great feature ideas here, we cannot build them all into Confluence core. There are, however, options within the [Atlassian Marketplace|https://marketplace.atlassian.com/search?application=confluence&category=&cost=&hosting=&marketingLabel=&q=translate] which provide this functionality. Thanks for all your feedback on jira.atlassian.com. Please keep your ideas coming.

Regards,
Bill Arconati
Confluence Group Product Manager
{panel}

