  {panel}

When an attachment is added, there should be a page modified action in the page's history.  This way you can see who added documents and when.  This would prevent someone from overriding an attachment without any log being generated.

Take the following code for example:

{color:red}Look Im red! {color:blue}Look Im blue!{color} Look Im red again!{color}

The output is: http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/TEST/What+color+am+I

Currently the work around is:

{color:red}Look Im red! {color}{color:blue}Look Im blue!{color}{color:red} Look Im red again!{color}

However, this may extend to other macro's nested, I haven tested extensively.
